I was in the same position but after some research and trial and error, I think I have a good solution in place. In order to demonstrate how to set things up, I'll build upon my [previous blog post](/blog/simple-build-step-for-netlify-functions/) that built a simple Netlify Function to print out Hello world followed by a random number.